-- 9:  HTTPS
-- 10: Rserved for future purposes
-- 11: Reserved for future purposes
-- 
-- 12: telnet
-- 13: ssh
-- 14: Reserved for future purposes
-- 15: Reserved for future purposes
-- 
-- 16: tftp
-- 17: ftp
-- 18: sftp
-- 19: scp
-- 
-- 20: Reserved for future purposes
-- ..
-- 31: Reserved for future purposes
-- 
